reason.raw: This model is not expected to be incorporated for the Cave Circuit to encourage teams to use alternate and multi-modal sensing approaches to overcome the challenges presented by noisy IMU data.

description.raw:
* Initial commit for x2c9 branch. This will be identical to x2 config 2 but with a nicer IMU.
* Updated the IMU model based off of the parameters in the ADIS16448 datasheet \([https://www.analog.com/media/en/technical-documentation/data-sheets/ADIS16488.pdf](https://www.analog.com/media/en/technical-documentation/data-sheets/ADIS16488.pdf)\)
* Details about how I came up with the parameters for this model are found here: \([#!/osrf/subt/issues/46/imu-details](#!/osrf/subt/issues/46/imu-details)\)

Originally submitted as ssci\_x2\_sensor\_config\_9.
